the former,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a sheep, or goat,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abogav","text_ar":"اَبْغَث"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the stalk, or twig, of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earofaj","text_ar":"عَرْفَج"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put forth its leaves, and what resembled nails"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aZaAfiyr","text_ar":"اَظَافِير"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"were seen in the place of separation"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mutafar~aq","text_ar":"مُتَفَرَّق"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of its stalks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twigs, and internodal portions;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓ the latter verb: (K, * TA:) this is said to be after what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tavoqiybN","text_ar":"تَثْقِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamalN","text_ar":"قَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and before what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idobaA='N","text_ar":"اـِدْبَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ixowaASN","text_ar":"اـِخْوَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or ↓ the latter verb, said of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Erfj","text_ar":"عرفج"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it put forth its leaves;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and this it does before its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idobaA='","text_ar":"اـِدْبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EarofajN","text_ar":"عَرْفَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] in a trad. occurs the expression"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArqAT~ EawosajuhaA","text_ar":"ارقاطّ عَوْسَجُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but El-Kutabee thinks that it should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EarofajuhaA","text_ar":"عَرْفَجُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n16369","headword_ar":"اَرْقَطُ","root":"rqT","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Black speckled with white:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the reverse:"},{"kind":"text","text":"fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqoTaA='u","text_ar":"رَقْطَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) Applied to a sheep or goat,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abogavu","text_ar":"اَبْغَثُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speckled with black and white."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 303.) And the fem., applied to a domestic fowl or hen ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dajaAjap","text_ar":"دَجَاجَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Black speckled with white:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party-coloured:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having patches of white and black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"much sought after, and used, by enchanters; and rarely found. (TA.) ―         -b2-  It is also applied to a man. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And the fem. is applied to a tract ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"risaAlapN","text_ar":"رِسَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), and to an ode ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSiydapN","text_ar":"قَصِيدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having one of the letters of a word thereof dotted, and another not dotted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"from the same epithet applied to a sheep or goat. (Har p. 303.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~ilosilapu Alr~aqoTaA='u","text_ar":"السِّلْسِلَةُ الرَّقْطَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain reptile; the most malignant of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of lizards called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiZaA='","text_ar":"عِظَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":":"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it crawls upon food, it poisons it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"variydapN raqoTaA='u","text_ar":"ثَرِيدَةٌ رَقْطَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mess of crumbled"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broken bread"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having much oil"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K *) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clarified butter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroqaTu","text_ar":"الاَرْقَطُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The leopard:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) an epithet in which the quality of a subst. predominates. (TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aqoTaA='u","text_ar":"الرَّقْطَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Civil war; conflict and faction; sedition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfitonapu","text_ar":"الفِتْنَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) because of its variableness: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is not universal;"},{"kind":"text","text":"likened to a speckled serpent: occurring in a trad. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}